[−][src]Enum rustup::dist::component::transaction::ChangedItem

enum ChangedItem<'a> {
    AddedFile(PathBuf),
    AddedDir(PathBuf),
    RemovedFile(PathBuf, File<'a>),
    RemovedDir(PathBuf, Dir<'a>),
    ModifiedFile(PathBuf, Option<File<'a>>),
}

This is the set of fundamental operations supported on a Transaction. More complicated operations, such as installing a package, or updating a component, distill down into a series of these primitives.
